1) compile the unit test class with other necessary classes:
javac -cp .:junit-4.12.jar -d . ./*.java

2) Run the unit test class by:
java -cp .:junit-4.12.jar:hamcrest-core-1.3.jar org.junit.runner.JUnitCore proj1a.DequeUnitTest
(here proj1a.DequeUnitTest is the package.class name)

More doc can be found:
https://github.com/junit-team/junit4/wiki

